PrecisAmendment to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS amending the definition of "prescribed share" for the purposes of the flow-through share program so that grants provided through the Ontario Mineral Incentive Program do not cause a share to be disqualified as a flow-through share.

Attachments
precis:
Amendment to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS amending the definition of
"prescribed share" for the purposes of the flow-through share program so
that grants provided through the Ontario Mineral Incentive Program do not
cause a share to be disqualified as a flow-through share.
